episodes.title: That one time a Serial Killer joined the Cult…
episodes.description:
Adam Rosenthal was on the run for murder. He joined the cult of the Twelve Tribes to hide out. He didn’t keep a low profile…he murdered one of the cult members. This is his story. 
Cash App: $JamieNickole77

episodes.title: The Yellow Deli…The restaurant that might just cost you your soul.
episodes.description: The Twelve Tribes is a religious cult that operates organic delis around the World. Eager to bring about the second coming of Christ, they beat the children, demean the women, pray for the death of the LGBTQIA+ community and have wild sexual practices.
